snippet.title: Ice Lakes Gameplay Trailer 1
snippet.description:
This is a video introducing game in the early alpha stage and do not represent the final quality. The final version of the game is now released and can be acquired from Steam.
http://store.steampowered.com/app/393430/


Ice Lakes is a modern fishing simulator with highly realistic sandbox approach to wintertime fishing.  Single and multiplayer with different game modes in the various sandbox locations around the world makes this game the ultimate ice fishing simulator. Master the use of wide selection of fishing gear and learn how changing season, bottom topology, day time and weather conditions affect fish behavior.
